           move      s-set                to   w-dpz-ide-set          .
           move      s-fas                to   w-dpz-ide-fas          .
           move      i-ide-des            to   w-dpz-ide-des          .
           move      s-pro                to   w-dpz-ide-pro          .
           call      "pgm/azi/prg/obj/pazi000d"
